## Read-Only Mode

For safety, restrict to read-only operations:
```json
{
  "args": ["-y", "@azure-devops/mcp@2.5.0", "MY_ORG", "--read-only"]
}
```
Or via header:
```json
{
  "headers": {
    "X-MCP-Readonly": "true"
  }
}
```

## Multiple Organizations

Configure separate instances per org:
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "ado-org1": {
      "args": ["-y", "@azure-devops/mcp@2.5.0", "ORG1"]
    },
    "ado-org2": {
      "args": ["-y", "@azure-devops/mcp@2.5.0", "ORG2"]
    }
  }
}
```

## Effective Prompts

**Include context:**
- Project name: "in project MyProject"
- Team name: "for team Backend"
- Time range: "in the last 7 days"
- State filters: "only active items"

**Avoid stale data:**
Add "Do not use previously fetched data" for fresh queries.

